<h2 id="latest-transport-statistics">Latest transport statistics</h2>

<p>14 March 2019:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics/driver-and-rider-testing-and-instructor-statistics-october-to-december-2018">Driver and rider testing and instructor statistics: October to December 2018</a></li>
</ul>

<p>13 March 2019:</p>

<ul>
