<h2 id="forthcoming-publications">Forthcoming publications</h2>

<p>This schedule gives the planned publication dates of all of the department’s annual, quarterly and compendium statistical releases for the coming year.</p>

<p>For reasons of brevity, we have omitted the monthly release of statistics on UK international sea passengers, <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/statistical-data-sets/sea-passenger-statistics-spas">SPAS0107</a>, usually released on the second Wednesday of each calendar month.</p>

